:eek: Project-DS v.6! needs you'r help! :eek: The forums are a fast crowing comunity! and i hope you all join and post We are looking out for testers,mods and admin on the server! Also posting on forums would improve the chance of keeping comunity up and growing! in two days we have has 138 members! THATS ALOT! Alot of people say that they will help but never turn up so i will ask for contact information please. E.G Msn,Aim,Yahoo. Cache Edier is SI FORCE special thanks to him! The server will handle all 471 items with 471 gameframe! Based in desert at the moment i will change if people are not fusset on it! I have currently added all teleporting to work! All combat level requaments [img]http://i193.photobucket.com/albums/z147/ownerhami/cc.jpg[/img] [img]http://i193.photobucket.com/albums/z147/ownerhami/cc1.jpg[/img] [img]http://i193.photobucket.com/albums/z147/ownerhami/cc2.jpg[/img] [img]http://i193.photobucket.com/albums/z147/ownerhami/cc3.jpg[/img] [img]http://i193.photobucket.com/albums/z147/ownerhami/cc4.jpg[img] [img]http://i193.photobucket.com/albums/z147/ownerhami/cc5.jpg[/img] [img]http://i193.photobucket.com/albums/z147/ownerhami/cc6.jpg[/img] Testers Mods Admins X-J-K-X i0wneveryone M,i,K,e
